<p>Market value measures the degree of user demand for tokens in the protocol. When users sell tokens, it indicates a decrease in demand for the tokens in the protocol, leading to a decrease in the token's market value. When users buy tokens, it indicates an increase in demand for the tokens in the protocol, leading to an increase in the token's market value.</p>
